we share the same goals.

589
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:48,680
Yes.

590
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:49,440
Indeed.

591
00:18:50,320 --> 00:18:51,080
So he usually...

592
00:18:51,560 --> 00:18:52,400
Ask instantly without any warm-up.

593
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:53,640
Instant questioning.

594
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:54,520
So he usually...

595
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:55,840
What kind of person do you think he is?

596
00:18:59,800 --> 00:19:01,360
What kind of person do I think he is?

597
00:19:01,360 --> 00:19:02,800
Let me think how to describe him.

598
00:19:04,120 --> 00:19:05,960
Would bros ever say nice things
to each other?

599
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:11,120
Silver saddle shining on white horse,
galloping swift as a shooting star.

600
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:13,760
Little Zhuoran.

601
00:19:13,760 --> 00:19:15,680
Just like a galloping horse.

602
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:18,200
Quite free.

603
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:19,320
Pursuing freedom?

604
00:19:19,320 --> 00:19:20,240
Not exactly pursuing freedom.

605
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:21,760
He has clear goals.

606
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:24,480
He still retains
a strong youthful spirit.

607
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,720
Of course, I think this is also

608
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:27,560
What attracts you to him.

609
00:19:30,600 --> 00:19:31,400
But she said

610
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,040
