611
00:19:32,040 --> 00:19:33,480
in the beginning.

612
00:19:33,480 --> 00:19:35,200
I think this is something quite normal.

613
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:37,400
That's because people's first impression

614
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:38,920
is often not correct.

615
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:41,640
Instead, after your communication,

616
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:43,400
your inner qualities
have attracted each other.

617
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:44,160
Yeah.

618
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:44,600
Right?

619
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:45,040
That's true.

620
00:19:45,040 --> 00:19:46,280
I think this should be better.

621
00:19:47,120 --> 00:19:47,680
But

622
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:49,560
during the process
of interacting with him,

623
00:19:50,080 --> 00:19:52,400
I found that all the points he made

624
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,640
were exactly what I wanted.

625
00:19:53,640 --> 00:19:54,520
Matching your expectations too well.

626
00:19:54,520 --> 00:19:56,560
So you're even less likely
to believe it.

627
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:56,880
Yeah.

628
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:58,520
It only means there's something magnetic
between you two.

629
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,800
I also want a friend like that.

630
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:13,040
Let's have something to eat.

631
00:20:13,040 --> 00:20:14,000
(Bro, hard work)
Eat and drink something.

632
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:14,880
Only I'm eating.

633
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:15,720
Have some beverage.

634
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:18,920
Sneaking a glance.

635
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:19,440
Sneaking a glance.

636
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:20,480
Am I right?

637
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:22,520
I memorized those two lines of poetry
all night.

638
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,520
Such a great talker.

639
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:27,720
That's why you're the real deal.

640
00:20:29,080 --> 00:20:30,560
Just ask whatever you want to ask.

641
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:32,280
After all, his best buddy is here.

642
00:20:32,280 --> 00:20:32,720
Yes.

643
00:20:33,360 --> 00:20:34,320
What about his past?

644
00:20:34,320 --> 00:20:35,400
His past relationships.

645
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:36,760
Oh, no!

646
00:20:36,760 --> 00:20:38,200
