Tell her.

649
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:46,560
No...

650
00:20:47,160 --> 00:20:47,800
You can tell her.

651
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:49,480
He is wiping sweat.

652
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:50,280
I know both of his ex-girlfriends.

653
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:51,840
You know both.

654
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:54,560
His first relationship was quite early.

655
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:56,640
Both of them

656
00:20:57,560 --> 00:20:59,280
