657
00:21:00,320 --> 00:21:01,680
So there were a lot of conflicts.

658
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:04,280
What about his second relationship?

659
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:05,520
The second one was because

660
00:21:05,520 --> 00:21:06,920
