661
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:07,720
What?

662
00:21:07,720 --> 00:21:09,400
What practical factors?

663
00:21:09,840 --> 00:21:11,320
Broke up because
of something in reality.

664
00:21:11,320 --> 00:21:13,400
Yeah, the girl

665
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:14,880
wanted to develop abroad,

666
00:21:16,080 --> 00:21:17,720
but he wanted to return.

667
00:21:18,320 --> 00:21:18,760
Yeah.

668
00:21:19,320 --> 00:21:20,600
Because of factors in reality,

669
00:21:20,600 --> 00:21:23,560
the general direction
and pace in the future

670
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:25,520
aren't quite aligned.

671
00:21:25,520 --> 00:21:27,080
If we can't even see each other,

672
00:21:27,080 --> 00:21:28,440
