673
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:29,840
Yeah, that's right.

674
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:31,480
Right.

675
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:34,200
They will also face
this long-distance issue.

676
00:21:42,720 --> 00:21:43,720
What are your plans for the future?

677
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:46,920
Well...

678
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:48,680
About how we interact in the future,

679
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:49,760
