680
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:50,840
How many times a month will you meet?

681
00:21:52,600 --> 00:21:53,400
How long will it be each time?

682
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:56,720
Right to the crucial point.

683
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:00,880
Am I being too realistic?

684
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:03,920
I think these questions

685
00:22:03,920 --> 00:22:05,000
are quite practical.

686
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:06,080
Yeah, I think it's a good thing.

687
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:07,640
A long-distance relationship.

688
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:10,160
I've never been
in a long-distance relationship before.

689
00:22:10,840 --> 00:22:11,600
You've never been
in a long-distance relationship?

690
00:22:13,480 --> 00:22:14,560
(It's so hard.)

691
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:16,080
(Too much pressure.)

692
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:18,520
Why are you sweating so profusely?

693
00:22:18,520 --> 00:22:19,640
Because it's too hot.

694
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:20,440
Thank you.

695
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:22,440
Excuse me, could you
turn down the AC a bit?

696
00:22:27,040 --> 00:22:28,000
He's under too much pressure.

697
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:28,400
Yes.

698
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:30,880
(I fell into a state)

699
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:32,800
(of confusion and deep thought again.)

700
00:22:32,800 --> 00:22:35,840
(I don't want Xihui
to give up anything for me.)

701
00:22:35,840 --> 00:22:37,160
(But I still want)

702
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:39,120
(to solve problems together with her)

703
00:22:39,120 --> 00:22:40,280
(while we slowly
get to know each other.)

704
00:22:41,120 --> 00:22:42,120
It's getting late, right?

705
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:43,320
Let's stop here.

706
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:44,520
We'll...

707
00:22:44,520 --> 00:22:46,080
I'll take her out for a walk
and look around.

708
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:47,600
Let me know when you get home.

709
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:49,320
Stay safe on the way.

710
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:49,800
Okay.

711
00:22:50,480 --> 00:22:51,320
Come visit Changsha.

712
00:22:52,040 --> 00:22:52,600
I definitely will.

713
00:22:53,120 --> 00:22:53,560
Okay.

714
00:22:58,280 --> 00:22:59,240
It's quite quiet.

715
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:03,720
Feeling a bit unhappy?

716
00:23:04,320 --> 00:23:04,760
Would you?

717
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:09,000
It's not that I'm unhappy.

718
00:23:09,000 --> 00:23:09,800
It's a bit complicated.

719
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:11,160
I understand.

720
00:23:14,280 --> 00:23:15,000
It's complicated.

721
00:23:16,032 --> 00:23:21,347
♪Time's moving so much slower lately♪

722
00:23:25,280 --> 00:23:26,320
We can walk a little slower.

723
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:27,160
I'm afraid you'll get tired.

724
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:30,400
Are your shoes pinching your feet?

725
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:30,640
No.

726
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:31,280
Rubbing?

727
00:23:31,280 --> 00:23:31,640
No.

728
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:39,000
This sea feels really different
from the sea

729
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:40,000
in Sanya.

730
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:40,440
Right.

731
00:23:40,440 --> 00:23:41,640
It feels very quiet.

732
00:23:42,520 --> 00:23:43,880
The sea in Sanya has waves.

733
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:47,040
Their states of mind are different now.

734
00:23:47,040 --> 00:23:48,840
Sanya was
about quickly getting them closer.

735
00:23:48,840 --> 00:23:50,040
Xiamen is about letting them
return to reality.

736
00:23:51,840 --> 00:23:52,160
Here?

737
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:52,920
Here?

738
00:23:53,360 --> 00:23:53,760
Yes.

739
00:23:53,760 --> 00:23:54,520
Let's sit here and rest for a while.

740
00:23:55,616 --> 00:24:00,608
♪That is until I touch you
and I can't pretend♪

741
00:24:00,608 --> 00:24:06,528
♪I lose myself again, I do♪

742
00:24:08,680 --> 00:24:09,800
Maintaining your posture.

743
00:24:15,584 --> 00:24:21,184
♪Can't back up♪

744
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:25,600
This city feels so quiet.

745
00:24:26,480 --> 00:24:27,680
Isn't Changsha also quiet?

746
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:30,480
Changsha is filled
with the haze of everyday life.

747
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:32,600
Haven't been there much.

748
00:24:33,920 --> 00:24:35,040
You can go and experience it.

749
00:24:36,240 --> 00:24:37,880
The real issues they wanted to discuss

750
00:24:37,880 --> 00:24:39,000
were never made clear.

751
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:40,640
They just instinctively avoided them.

752
00:24:44,280 --> 00:24:46,200
Well, is there anything
you want to know about me?

753
00:24:46,200 --> 00:24:47,360
Nothing I really...

754
00:24:47,360 --> 00:24:48,640
Currently, I have no questions.

755
00:24:52,520 --> 00:24:54,680
Maybe the only issue is

756
00:24:55,520 --> 00:24:56,320
