757
00:24:58,000 --> 00:24:59,400
I would realize

758
00:25:01,320 --> 00:25:04,240
that Xiamen is still my home.

759
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:06,360
Maybe my roots are here.

760
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:08,640
In my career, I will

761
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:09,760
go out and strive.

762
00:25:09,760 --> 00:25:11,120
But most likely, I will

763
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:13,480
still choose to stay in this place.

764
00:25:15,040 --> 00:25:17,640
He doesn't want to go to another city.

765
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:18,720
Oh, no.

766
00:25:25,840 --> 00:25:28,160
I realized
that once I enter a relationship,

767
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:29,720
I'd become not like myself.

768
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:33,840
I'd become anxious
about gains and losses.

769
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:35,200
I'd start overthinking a lot.

770
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:36,480
I'd think too much.

771
00:25:40,360 --> 00:25:41,880
But what hasn't changed about me is

772
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:42,600
that I would still

773
00:25:43,520 --> 00:25:44,440
offer

774
00:25:46,360 --> 00:25:47,720
