775
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:52,560
Are you afraid of getting hurt?

776
00:25:55,120 --> 00:25:56,600
How can we avoid getting hurt?

777
00:25:57,880 --> 00:25:59,360
It's easy to get hurt in relationships.

778
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:03,320
But being brave will only...

779
00:26:04,320 --> 00:26:04,920
Being brave...

780
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:06,880
Being brave means leaving no regrets.

781
00:26:06,880 --> 00:26:07,640
Yeah.

782
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:09,800
It will only bring good things,
no bad things.

783
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:13,600
(Love is a game for the brave.)

784
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:15,800
Don't you think so?

785
00:26:19,600 --> 00:26:21,200
You need to appreciate yourself enough.

786
00:26:25,320 --> 00:26:26,640
And maximize your sense of worthiness.

787
00:26:31,840 --> 00:26:33,400
You are always the most worthy one.

788
00:26:36,120 --> 00:26:36,480
Am I right?

789
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:45,120
Later...

790
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:47,440
What do you usually do after this?

791
00:26:50,280 --> 00:26:52,000
Just casually

792
00:26:55,560 --> 00:26:56,320
drive around,

793
00:26:56,880 --> 00:26:58,120
turn the music volume to the max,

794
00:26:58,640 --> 00:26:59,320
and

795
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:01,560
not think about anything.

796
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:03,520
Then,

797
00:27:05,240 --> 00:27:06,240
just go home.

798
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:08,200
(This girl is looking at him
very earnestly.)

799
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:08,800
(Yes.)

800
00:27:08,800 --> 00:27:10,280
Well, we're full now.

801
00:27:10,280 --> 00:27:10,960
We can't drink

802
00:27:10,960 --> 00:27:12,000
or eat anything else.

803
00:27:13,880 --> 00:27:14,520
I'm done for.

804
00:27:15,360 --> 00:27:15,840
Why?

805
00:27:16,280 --> 00:27:17,440
Completely done for.

806
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,000
Why?

807
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:19,800
I mean me.

808
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:20,840
Why?

809
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:22,880
Why are you done for?

810
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:24,040
She's fallen for him.

811
00:27:24,040 --> 00:27:25,880
Is that what she means or what?

812
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:27,360
What do you mean?

813
00:27:29,600 --> 00:27:30,600
Why are you done for?

814
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:31,880
Completely done for.

815
00:27:36,800 --> 00:27:37,200
I don't get it.

816
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:38,760
What's the matter?

817
00:27:38,760 --> 00:27:39,800
Wasn't everything going smoothly today?

818
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:42,800
I said I'm done for.

819
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:43,080
Why?

820
00:27:43,080 --> 00:27:45,320
I didn't say this trip was done for.

821
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:46,440
Why?

822
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:51,040
I can't bring myself to say it.

823
00:27:57,600 --> 00:27:58,400
Why?

824
00:27:59,800 --> 00:28:01,000
(I was looking at his profile.)

825
00:28:01,520 --> 00:28:03,480
(At that moment,
I just felt I really liked him.)

826
00:28:05,080 --> 00:28:06,680
Am I not completely done for?

827
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:08,400
She likes him.

828
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:09,320
She likes him.

829
00:28:09,320 --> 00:28:10,440
She knows there is
a long-distance issue.

830
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:12,520
But she feels she really likes him.

831
00:28:12,520 --> 00:28:13,440
She's fallen.

832
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,080
Yes.

833
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:17,600
(She looked at him
for a long time without speaking.)

834
00:28:17,600 --> 00:28:18,880
(Then she finally said, "I'm done for.")

835
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:21,000
(This is so touching.)

836
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:21,880
(So cool.)

837
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:23,400
(This is really moving.)

838
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:24,400
(Really moving.)

839
00:28:29,080 --> 00:28:29,680
I get it now.

840
00:28:30,560 --> 00:28:31,680
Swept off your feet by me.

841
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:34,080
I'm speechless.

842
00:28:34,080 --> 00:28:34,840
I'm going home.

843
00:28:35,360 --> 00:28:36,240
My plane has arrived.

844
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:36,720
I'll hurry.

845
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:38,840
Just kidding.

846
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:40,160
My plane has arrived.

847
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:40,760
I'm leaving right away.

848
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:46,000
How could you say it yourself?

849
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:50,640
Love shatters certain things.

850
00:28:50,640 --> 00:28:51,440
Yeah.

851
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:53,200
She actually cared about him so much.

852
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:54,240
She said she was in Xiamen.

853
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:55,440
But she also said, "I'm done for."

854
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:55,880
Yes.

855
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:57,160
(I heard such a cruel answer,)

856
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:58,280
(but I still like you.)

857
00:28:58,280 --> 00:29:00,200
(Yeah, I can't help it.)

858
00:29:00,200 --> 00:29:01,680
(I still like you.)

859
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:03,280
A moth.

860
00:29:05,120 --> 00:29:06,120
A moth flying into the flame.

