the side we want the most?

1524
00:55:20,680 --> 00:55:23,280
And that should be fulfilling,

1525
00:55:23,280 --> 00:55:24,320
enjoyable enough.

1526
00:55:24,880 --> 00:55:25,840
You must enjoy it fully.

1527
00:55:25,840 --> 00:55:27,160
Life must be lived to the fullest.

1528
00:55:27,760 --> 00:55:29,920
In this life,
you must live it to the fullest,

1529
00:55:30,360 --> 00:55:31,232
