1560
00:56:44,960 --> 00:56:46,600
Actually, if you think about it,
this is love.

1561
00:56:46,600 --> 00:56:47,960
Love was never that grand to begin with.

1562
00:56:49,280 --> 00:56:50,208
Is that so?

1563
00:56:51,080 --> 00:56:52,760
So those feelings are all valid.

1564
00:56:52,760 --> 00:56:53,680
They are valid.

1565
00:56:53,680 --> 00:56:54,640
Because having these feelings

1566
00:56:54,640 --> 00:56:56,120
