1585
00:57:29,360 --> 00:57:30,920
As for the rest...

1586
00:57:31,680 --> 00:57:34,240
The people in the house,

1587
00:57:34,240 --> 00:57:35,296
maybe everyone will

1588
00:57:36,288 --> 00:57:37,280
more or less

1589
00:57:37,280 --> 00:57:38,160
