1590
00:57:38,160 --> 00:57:39,280
and I think it's reasonable.

1591
00:57:39,280 --> 00:57:40,720
Just leave it to life, to ourselves.

1592
00:57:40,720 --> 00:57:42,680
Getting along easily and happily,

1593
00:57:42,680 --> 00:57:44,560
I think is the first principle

1594
00:57:44,560 --> 00:57:46,160
- of all relationships.
- Yes.

1595
00:57:46,160 --> 00:57:47,000
Emotions.

1596
00:57:47,000 --> 00:57:48,600
They are actually not abstract.

1597
00:57:48,600 --> 00:57:49,600
