and

1604
00:58:01,120 --> 00:58:02,880
all kinds of

1605
00:58:04,840 --> 00:58:06,720
- feelings.
- Yes.

1606
00:58:06,720 --> 00:58:07,920
- They will be triggered.
- Yes.

1607
00:58:08,520 --> 00:58:10,360
You can't just live as your superego.

1608
00:58:10,360 --> 00:58:11,840
Right, that would be too exhausting.

1609
00:58:11,840 --> 00:58:13,880
- That would be too exhausting.
- Yes.

1610
00:58:13,880 --> 00:58:14,720
But I think,

1611
00:58:14,720 --> 00:58:15,920
about these

1612
00:58:16,520 --> 00:58:18,000
