(I really like this saying.)

1620
00:58:30,480 --> 00:58:32,440
Two wise people are talking.

1621
00:58:36,736 --> 00:58:37,720
The last part was very...

1622
00:58:37,720 --> 00:58:38,600
It was quite healing.

1623
00:58:38,600 --> 00:58:39,744
Very healing.

1624
00:58:39,920 --> 00:58:41,160
I think love triggers

1625
