1627
00:58:44,960 --> 00:58:46,680
That's also a beautiful side.

1628
00:58:47,080 --> 00:58:48,160
For Danqi,

1629
00:58:48,160 --> 00:58:50,320
what happened today

1630
00:58:50,320 --> 00:58:52,760
