1631
00:58:52,760 --> 00:58:53,840
but it actually taught her to grow.

1632
00:58:54,600 --> 00:58:55,560
And I feel

1633
00:58:55,560 --> 00:58:56,880
that if you dare to show

1634
00:58:56,880 --> 00:58:57,960
the so-called

1635
00:58:57,960 --> 00:58:59,240
