1640
00:59:05,040 --> 00:59:05,960
That, I think,

1641
00:59:05,960 --> 00:59:08,080
is not conducive to a deep relationship

1642
00:59:08,080 --> 00:59:08,920
for long-term development.

1643
00:59:08,920 --> 00:59:09,920
Yes.

1644
00:59:09,920 --> 00:59:10,920
Zick Rubin said

1645
00:59:10,920 --> 00:59:12,320
