1647
00:59:14,240 --> 00:59:16,280
One is the emotion of helping others.

1648
00:59:16,280 --> 00:59:18,600
Your altruism will be especially strong.

1649
00:59:18,600 --> 00:59:21,480
The other one is called
exclusive possessiveness.

1650
00:59:21,480 --> 00:59:22,440
You want to make them

1651
00:59:22,440 --> 00:59:23,760
