1657
00:59:30,520 --> 00:59:32,400
They are really

1658
00:59:32,400 --> 00:59:33,920
the two inseparable sides of love.

1659
00:59:35,560 --> 00:59:37,320
I think we are all just ordinary people.

1660
00:59:37,320 --> 00:59:38,240
Yes.

1661
00:59:38,240 --> 00:59:40,600
There's no need to detach
from the daily necessities of life

1662
00:59:40,600 --> 00:59:42,960
